title: Выхожу тебя искать
overview: Mikhail and Denis Demirov work in the department for searching for missing persons. The brothers are absolutely not alike - neither in character, nor in habits, nor in their attitude to life. Psychologist Rita Vysotskaya comes to work in their department. And soon both brothers find themselves drawn into a complex love triangle. Mikhail and Denis do not realize that Rita has a secret. The girl works in the department with one goal - she wants to "find herself": Rita does not know her real name, she remembers herself only from the moment she was hit by a car in a small provincial town
